{"id": 1891, "genre": 1000, "title": "现如今你有哪些视觉盲区？", "description": "互联网探照灯照不到的地方，我都看不见。(题图来自：pixabay）", "record_count": 7686, "comment_count": 20, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170905133138UWecurIJqEfoPVQh.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-09-07T17:00:36Z", "questions": [{"id": 2920, "title": "现如今你有哪些视觉盲区？", "content": "现如今你有哪些视觉盲区？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 233796, "content": "平时根本不会注意家门口的小馆子，美食公众号推过之后才赶紧去尝", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132014rcm6wbFZO8i3JtzY.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233797, "content": " 看电影、剧、综艺，很少看影评类博主没推荐过的", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132040JQ0rUCYulqvGdh6P.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233798, "content": "关注微博知乎上的儿童性侵，对身边遭受欺凌的人却很钝感", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132058eoS429xgk7vdiQrJ.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233799, "content": "聚合app里文章来源都一样，只是换着地方看同样的内容，没有新东西", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132133BeCNir1vZtyMaup2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233800, "content": "买护肤品只买网红款，没听过的品牌产品都是隐形的", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132204gRmYxfier5dHhaMo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233801, "content": "关于政治的讨论趋于庸俗化八卦化，公共政策啥的了解非常少", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132217MX0xuOor2EZFVIAU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233802, "content": " 公众人物的风评一边倒，看了网友列的“罪状”就形成固定印象", "image": "img/option/option/20170905132242FGszHTER7uM4OLwo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 233803, "content": "听音乐，一个传奇音乐人去世了才开始听 ta 的歌", "image": "img/option/option/201709051326446gT3akm1fFoHlrIt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}